Miiko Taka https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miiko_Taka 0 Miiko Taka (高美以子, Taka Miiko) (born Miiko Shikata June 24, 1925), is a Japanese American actress best known for co-starring with Marlon Brando as Hana-ogi in the 1957 movie Sayonara.
